      <p>
        <strong>Los Caballos Mobile Equine Veterinary Services</strong><br>
        24/7 emergency equine veterinary care — mobile, comes to your property<br>
        Phone: <a href="tel:+19286366644">(928) 636-6644</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Olsen's Grain — Dewey location</strong><br>
        Feed, hay, and ranch supplies for horses and livestock; hay delivery available<br>
        ~15 miles from Goswick Ranch via AZ-69
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Prescott Livestock Auction</strong><br>
        Chino Valley, AZ — Regular auctions for cattle, horses, goats, and sheep
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Mark Goswick Cattle Co.</strong><br>
        Bloody Basin Road area · <a href="tel:+19286327730">(928) 632-7730</a><br>
        The continuing legacy of the Goswick family cattle ranching tradition in the valley below the subdivision.
      </p>

      <h2>Community Events</h2>
      <p><strong>Mayer Daze</strong> — Annual festival held each October at the Mayer Recreation Center. Free admission. Events include a parade, BBQ, classic car show, vendor booths, and live entertainment. Running since approximately 1961.</p>

